data.description: The perfect blend of impressive essentials & contemporary updates! The naturally lit family room, casual dining space, & kitchen seamlessly blend together. The kitchen boasts SS appliances & two-toned cabinets. Retreat to the primary bedroom, with vaulted ceilings & private ensuite/walk-in closet. Down the hall are two comfortable guest bedrooms, a versatile loft, a full hall bathroom, & convenient laundry room; all with A/C. Unwind in the fully fenced, serene backyard. Ample off-street & driveway parking plus a two-car garage. The Avery Park neighborhood is only moments away from outdoor recreation, highways, local eateries, and shopping. Plus, enjoy the tight-knit community lifestyle without an HOA.
